headline: NHS must pay ‘fair share’, says US drug giant amid Trump pressure
summary: The NHS must pay more towards new drug development to help cut prices for Americans, a major US pharmaceutical giant has said.

headline: Bristol Myers Squibb Commits to Veeva Vault CRM
summary: Veeva Systems (NYSE: VEEV) today announced that Bristol Myers Squibb (BMS) has committed to Veeva Vault CRM.

headline: MapLight lines up an IPO in bid to challenge Bristol Myers schizophrenia drug
summary: The company, which is developing a competitor to Cobenfy, aims to become one of rare biotechs to price a large IPO of late.
